{"tid":2101215,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［又一單］警員18205 承認同袍收慢腳步而非遭被告阻擋去路 被告沒有不斷掙扎 只係我誤會左","createTime":"2020-07-09T15:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T01:28:05.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f0c76288d29fb54d95723279f8507077c938e0f2","tid":2101215,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T15:25:56.000Z","msg":"自稱受阻的警員18205供稱被告當日明言「唔X走」，並且放慢腳步，令他及身旁兩名同袍跟不上推進步伐。惟當控方要求他澄清被告如何能以一人阻三人時，警員承認同袍是自己收慢腳步、而非遭被告阻擋去路。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警方及傳媒片段顯示被告遭制服後並無反抗或掙扎，惟警員在事後口供紙上稱被告「不斷掙扎」。辯方就此質問警員，警員承認當時看不到被告掙扎，但因現場環境混亂，以為被告有掙扎，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">「可能我誤會咗」，但否認作出虛假陳述。</span></span></strong>聆訊明續。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200709/AUO7I3A4MXNF5QI6Q7X5NNXX4Y/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200709%2FAUO7I3A4MXNF5QI6Q7X5NNXX4Y%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsju4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=3a22dcc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200709%2FAUO7I3A4MXNF5QI6Q7X5NNXX4Y%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=b0185a4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200709/AUO7I3A4MXNF5QI6Q7X5NNXX4Y/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"625f84b9ef9dd0d6873287959f798ee427259260","tid":2101215,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T15:27:38.000Z","msg":"唔講以為被告係架坦克車<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e142af1625a10d28003a6b40402a1ea15f8f7872","tid":2101215,"uid":44083,"like":0,"